{"title":"This Room and Everything in It","author":{"name":"Li-Young Lee"},"publishDate":"2005-09-23","lines":[{"line":"Lie still now","stanza":1,"number":1},{"line":"while I prepare for my future,","stanza":1,"number":2},{"line":"certain hard days ahead,","stanza":1,"number":3},{"line":"when I’ll need what I know so clearly this moment.","stanza":1,"number":4},{"line":"I am making use","stanza":2,"number":5},{"line":"of the one thing I learned","stanza":2,"number":6},{"line":"of all the things my father tried to teach me:","stanza":2,"number":7},{"line":"the art of memory.","stanza":2,"number":8},{"line":"I am letting this room","stanza":3,"number":9},{"line":"and everything in it","stanza":3,"number":10},{"line":"stand for my ideas about love","stanza":3,"number":11},{"line":"and its difficulties.","stanza":3,"number":12},{"line":"I’ll let your love-cries,","stanza":4,"number":13},{"line":"those spacious notes","stanza":4,"number":14},{"line":"of a moment ago,","stanza":4,"number":15},{"line":"stand for distance.","stanza":4,"number":16},{"line":"Your scent,","stanza":5,"number":17},{"line":"that scent","stanza":5,"number":18},{"line":"of spice and a wound,","stanza":5,"number":19},{"line":"I’ll let stand for mystery.","stanza":5,"number":20},{"line":"Your sunken belly","stanza":6,"number":21},{"line":"is the daily cup","stanza":6,"number":22},{"line":"of milk I drank","stanza":6,"number":23},{"line":"as a boy before morning prayer.","stanza":6,"number":24},{"line":"The sun on the face","stanza":7,"number":25},{"line":"of the wall","stanza":7,"number":26},{"line":"is God, the face","stanza":7,"number":27},{"line":"I can’t see, my soul,","stanza":7,"number":28},{"line":"and so on, each thing","stanza":8,"number":29},{"line":"standing for a separate idea,","stanza":8,"number":30},{"line":"and those ideas forming the constellation","stanza":8,"number":31},{"line":"of my greater idea.","stanza":8,"number":32},{"line":"And one day, when I need","stanza":8,"number":33},{"line":"to tell myself something intelligent","stanza":8,"number":34},{"line":"about love,","stanza":8,"number":35},{"line":"I’ll close my eyes","stanza":9,"number":36},{"line":"and recall this room and everything in it:","stanza":9,"number":37},{"line":"My body is estrangement.","stanza":9,"number":38},{"line":"This desire, perfection.","stanza":9,"number":39},{"line":"Your closed eyes my extinction.","stanza":9,"number":40},{"line":"Now I’ve forgotten my","stanza":9,"number":41},{"line":"idea. The book","stanza":9,"number":42},{"line":"on the windowsill, riffled by wind…","stanza":9,"number":43},{"line":"the even-numbered pages are","stanza":9,"number":44},{"line":"the past, the odd-","stanza":9,"number":45},{"line":"numbered pages, the future.","stanza":9,"number":46},{"line":"The sun is","stanza":9,"number":47},{"line":"God, your body is milk…","stanza":9,"number":48},{"line":"useless, useless…","stanza":10,"number":49},{"line":"your cries are song, my body’s not me…","stanza":10,"number":50},{"line":"no good…my idea","stanza":10,"number":51},{"line":"has evaporated…your hair is time, your thighs are song…","stanza":10,"number":52},{"line":"it had something to do","stanza":10,"number":53},{"line":"with death…it had something","stanza":10,"number":54},{"line":"to do with love.","stanza":10,"number":55}]}